*** ChanServ Help - Command: SET WELCOME ***
Changes the channel's Welcome Notice. If it is set,
ChanServ will send a notice to anyone joining the
channel. By default, no welcome message is used.
When NONE is specified the Welcome Message will be disabled.
 
Syntax:
/cs SET #channel WELCOME message
 
Examples:
/cs SET #IRCHelp WELCOME Welcome to #IRCHelp!
/cs SET #Services WELCOME NONE
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***